snippet.title: Touhou 4: Lotus Land Story - Stage 3 (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
Interior of the drained lake

All in all stage 3 is a bit simpler than stage 2 the enemies that show up are either there solely to be blasted away or have fairly predictable attacking patterns.

Your primary worries are a couple moves both the mid-boss and Elly will pull off however so long as you go out of your way to make sure you don't get cornered you'll be fine.

In general when dealing with Elly you have to make sure you have room to escape just in case because she'll constantly be throwing her scythe at you while shooting her bullet patterns

Watch this video's gonna shoot up to my most watched solely because Bad Apple's in the description...

Difficulty - Normal
Character - Marisa-A ~ Illusion Laser
Stage 3 - Darkness ~ Darkness
BGM - BAD Apple!! 
Boss - Gatekeeper of the Mansion: Elly
BGM - Spirit Battle ~ Perdition crisis 

Translation's courtesy of the Touhou wiki
